OL,3,CAnti-Terror Traffic Order in place
OL,4,Cduring York Christmas Market
OL,6,FOnly emergency services will be
OL,7,Fallowed into the centre of York during
OL,8,Fthe Christmas Market period because of
OL,9,Fa new restriction from police.
OL,11,FNorth Yorkshire Police recommended
OL,12,FYork Council put an Anti-Terror
OL,13,FTraffic Regulation Order in place for
OL,14,Fsafety reasons. This stops all
OL,15,Fvehicles, other than emergency
OL,16,Fservices, from entering the city
OL,17,Fcentre from 10am to 7pm.
