OL,3,CAnti-Terror Traffic Order in place
OL,4,Cduring York Christmas Market
OL,6,FPreviously Blue Badge holders and
OL,7,Fspecific vehicles like delivery vans
OL,8,Fand waste collectors were allowed in,
OL,9,Fbut that won't be the case this year.
OL,11,FThe order will be in force from
OL,12,FThursday 13 November until Saturday 21
OL,13,FDecember - covering all York city
OL,14,Fcentre streets currently subject to
OL,15,Fhostile vehicle measures.
OL,17,FChief Constable Tim Forber said the
OL,18,Fmeasures are needed to protect against
OL,19,Fterror attacks during the event which
OL,20,Fdraws thousands of extra visitors to
OL,21,Fthe city.
