OL,3,CAnti-Terror Traffic Order in place
OL,4,Cduring York Christmas Market
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 7 October the request was
OL,7,Fapproved unanimously by councillors.
OL,9,FIn his letter to the council, Chief
OL,10,FConstable Forber said a number of
OL,11,Fattacks involving vehicles had taken
OL,12,Fplace in the last year including in
OL,13,FNew Orleans and Liverpool.
