OL,3,CAnti-Terror Traffic Order in place
OL,4,Cduring York Christmas Market
OL,6,FThe chief constable said: "These
OL,7,Fincidents, teamed with the rise in
OL,8,Fpolitical tensions means there is a
OL,9,Fneed to consider the vulnerability of
OL,10,FYork Christmas Market to a similar
OL,11,Fattack and ensure all security
OL,12,Fmeasures are put in place and
OL,13,Fstringently adhered to.
OL,15,F"Any exemptions to these measures
OL,16,Fwould increase the risk and
OL,17,Fvulnerability to an attack, determined
OL,18,Fattackers will seek to exploit any
OL,19,Fweaknesses to gain access to the
OL,20,Fprotected area.
