OL,6,F"These measures are proportionate and
OL,7,Fnecessary to support the safety and
OL,8,Feffective management of the event and
OL,9,Fthese restrictions form a critical
OL,10,Felement for the collective approach to
OL,11,Favoid and reduce the likelihood of
OL,12,Fdanger connected with terrorism."
OL,14,FThe council's report stated that
OL,15,Falthough the risk of an attack may
OL,16,Fseem low, if one happened it would be
OL,17,F"catastrophic".
