OL,6,FIt stated: "Depending on the event in
OL,7,Fquestion, were any serious failings to
OL,8,Fbe identified as a result of such an
OL,9,Fincident, the council may be subject
OL,10,Fto a public inquiry process, criminal
OL,11,Fcharges, and reputational damage as
OL,12,Fwell as the wider impact on the wider
OL,13,Feconomy."
OL,15,FCllr Katie Lomas (Labour, Acomb Ward)
OL,16,Fsaid "safe access for all" needs to be
OL,17,Fthe primary concern.
OL,19,FShe said: "I'm devastated we're in
OL,20,Fthis position, but we need to make
OL,21,Ftough decisions.
